HISTORICAL NOTE:

This is a modern Go port of the classic 1980s text adventure game "Zork I:
The Great Underground Empire" originally created by Infocom, Inc. The game's
source code in ZIL (Zork Implementation Language) was released as open source
by Microsoft Corporation in 2025 under the MIT License for historical
preservation purposes.

This implementation faithfully recreates the original game mechanics, puzzles,
and content while providing a modern, cross-platform executable. All original
game text, descriptions, and narrative content remain copyrighted to their
respective owners and are used here for historical preservation and
educational purposes under the terms of the MIT License.
